AZContains.meaning: This indicates that the parent object contains the child object, such as a resource group containing a virtual machine, or a tenant containing a subscription. Control of the parent object also gives control of the child object.
AZContains.common: 不可直接利用 - 此关系表示对象包含层次结构，控制父对象即可控制子对象，但本身不是攻击技术
